<lb n="5"/>tiruccūlattāpaṉam paṇṇi pūcaiyum tiruppaṇiyum naṭattuvippatu Ivai <hi rend="grantha">rā</hi>kutta<hi rend="grantha">rā</hi>maṉ Eḻuttu <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="danda">.</g></supplied>
